    <link href="http://noppanit.github.io/the-best-hot-chocolate/"/>
    <updated>2008-03-29T00:00:00-04:00</updated>
    <id>http://noppanit.github.io/the-best-hot-chocolate</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This is the best chocolate I have ever taste.</p>

<p>Ingredients<br/>
1. Chocolate powder<br/>
2. Semi-skimmed milk<br/>
3. Chocolate moose</p>

<ol>
<li>Simmer semi-skimmed milk until you can see a little bubbles come out, but not boil it until the boiling point</li>
<li>2 tablespoons of chocolate powder and add the simmering milk</li>
<li>decorate chocolate moose on top of the chocolate milk</li>
<li>sprinkle a little bit of chocolate powder as in the picture</li>
</ol>


